findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeToWhiteList(), setLimits(), addPrivateSalers(), removePrivateSalers(), addExcludedFromLimits(), removeExcludedFromLimits(), and multiSendTokens() use loops that can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the input lists are too long.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges even after ownership renouncement, allowing them to perform various actions such as enabling/disabling trading, changing fees and addresses, and withdrawing tokens.
